    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1174">
<l>peyalāṟṟā nīrulanta vuṇka ṇuyalāṟṟā </l>
<l> vuyviṉō yeṉkaṇ niṟuttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These painted eyes have caused me a lasting mortal disease; and now they can weep no more, the tears having dried up.</l>
            </lg>
